36
00:04:10,333 --> 00:04:11,459
Oh, are you alright?

37
00:04:12,627 --> 00:04:14,003
Oh, shut up!

38
00:04:21,177 --> 00:04:22,512
[Melvin] Where you from Peewee?

39
00:04:23,346 --> 00:04:24,472
[Unico] I don't know.

40
00:04:27,642 --> 00:04:28,768
Where you headed?

41
00:04:30,144 --> 00:04:31,562
I don't know.

42
00:04:33,982 --> 00:04:36,901
I never met anybody before
who didn't know where

43
00:04:36,943 --> 00:04:39,112
