57
00:05:13,187 --> 00:05:16,441
-I'm Unico, that's all I know.
-[screams] Stay away from me!

58
00:05:16,441 --> 00:05:19,444
-Get back!
-I'm not going to do anything.

59
00:05:19,444 --> 00:05:20,820
That's what you say.

60
00:05:21,571 --> 00:05:23,990
What's that horn
doing on your head?

61
00:05:24,115 --> 00:05:26,284
Oh, oh, oh.
[electronic squeak]

62
00:05:27,702 --> 00:05:30,246
