-Yeah! Stay away from me. Oh!

65
00:05:37,295 --> 00:05:40,965
[gasping] Go ahead, kill me,
I'm all yours, get it over with.

66
00:05:41,174 --> 00:05:42,884
[sobs] I'm so young.

67
00:05:42,884 --> 00:05:44,719
