ahead of me.

68
00:05:44,844 --> 00:05:47,847
-[sobbing continues]
-Now then,

69
00:05:48,097 --> 00:05:50,808
-Huh?
-Take a good look at that guy

70
00:05:50,808 --> 00:05:52,477
-you're so scared of.
-What?

71
00:05:53,519 --> 00:05:56,898
You know, when you start falling
like a baby in front of a midget

72
00:05:56,898 --> 00:06:00,318
