74
00:06:02,362 --> 00:06:03,654
[stutters] But his horn?

75
00:06:03,738 --> 00:06:05,782
Eh, it's the size
of a toothpick,

76
00:06:05,782 --> 00:06:07,492
it couldn't harm a flea.

77
00:06:08,159 --> 00:06:09,619
[gasps] Oh-uh.

78
00:06:10,078 --> 00:06:11,412
Watch out! [groans]

79
00:06:13,790 --> 00:06:15,833
-What's the big idea?
-Hm?

80
00:06:15,875 --> 00:06:18,211
Thought you could pull
a fast one on me, did ya?

81
00:06:18,961 --> 00:06:21,714
-Hm? Mm.
-[gasping] Oh, oh.

82
00:06:22,173 --> 00:06:25,176
Ha-ha, you're not so tough
after all, are you?

83
00:06:25,385 --> 00:06:28,679
I'll teach you to make a fool
outta Melvin Manificat.

84
00:06:28,888 --> 00:06:33,267
-[gasps] Ow, ow.
-[screams] I'm gonna kill you!

85
00:06:36,354 --> 00:06:40,108
I'm gonna turn that horn
of yours into mandolin picks.

86
00:06:40,733 --> 00:06:43,403
Stop right where you are Peewee!

87
00:06:43,403 --> 00:06:45,238
-I won't.
-[screaming continues]

88
00:06:47,949 --> 00:06:51,869
Okay, that does it,
now you made me mad.

89
00:06:52,286 --> 00:06:54,539
-[chuckles]
-There he goes.

90
00:06:54,956 --> 00:06:56,457
[gasps and screams]

91
00:06:57,166 --> 00:07:00,211
If he knows what's good for him,
he'll clear out of my forest,

92
00:07:00,211 --> 00:07:02,588
-and pronto. Come on.
-You handled that real good.

93
00:07:02,630 --> 00:07:04,632
Well, that's what a boss
is for after all.

94
00:07:04,632 --> 00:07:05,883
Yeah, that's true enough.

