00:07:17,937 --> 00:07:18,938
[groans]

98
00:07:20,940 --> 00:07:23,734
He told me to get
out of his forest.

99
00:07:24,735 --> 00:07:27,196
But I don't' know
which way is out.

100
00:07:29,157 --> 00:07:30,158
Hm?

101
00:07:34,120 --> 00:07:35,121
[lightening]

102
00:07:43,171 --> 00:07:46,090
Hi, I'm Unico, who are you?

103
00:07:46,549 --> 00:07:47,550
[sighs]

104
00:07:53,055 --> 00:07:54,056
Huh?

105
00:07:54,432 --> 00:07:56,684
Hi, I'm Unico.

106
00:07:57,643 --> 00:08:01,355
Oh, nobody seems to
like me in this forest.

107
00:08:48,486 --> 00:08:49,487
[flute music]

108
00:08:51,864 --> 00:08:52,865
Huh?

109
00:09:00,706 --> 00:09:01,707
[music continues]

110
00:09:07,088 --> 00:09:08,089
[wind howling]

111
00:09:24,272 --> 00:09:25,273
[flute crescendo]

112
00:09:42,832 --> 00:09:43,833
[squeaks]

113
00:10:21,704 --> 00:10:22,705
[music continues]

114
00:10:32,173 --> 00:10:33,841
-[Melvin growling]
-Huh?

115
00:10:34,759 --> 00:10:38,012
-[gasps]
-[growls] What's that guy

116
00:10:38,054 --> 00:10:42,391
thinking he's trying to muscle
his way into my territory.

117
00:10:42,391 --> 00:10:46,228
-[growls]
-It's kinda nice music, ya know.

118
00:10:46,354 --> 00:10:49,815
It almost makes you
wanna cry, don't it? [gasps]

119
00:10:53,486 --> 00:10:58,157
[shouts] Hey you! That's it,
the party's over, knock it off.

120
00:11:00,076 --> 00:11:02,453
-[squeaks]
-That's better, now take that

121
00:11:02,495 --> 00:11:04,622
little flute of yours
and fly away.

122
00:11:04,789 --> 00:11:06,123
Get outta here!

123
00:11:06,749 --> 00:11:09,251
Hey! Did you hear me?
[electronic swish]

124
00:11:10,753 --> 00:11:11,754
Huh?

125
00:11:13,422 --> 00:11:15,966
Who is that guy?

126
00:11:16,967 --> 00:11:20,971
Hey! Put an egg in your shoe
and beat it, you heard the boss,

127
00:11:21,013 --> 00:11:22,390
get lost!

128
00:11:24,600 --> 00:11:25,601
[electronic crescendo]

129
00:11:27,978 --> 00:11:28,979
[electronic swiping]

130
00:11:31,399 --> 00:11:32,400
[all groan]

131
00:11:39,240 --> 00:11:42,159
Huh? What's going on?

132
00:11:43,953 --> 00:11:44,954
[screams]

133
00:11:48,040 --> 00:11:49,875
Hey, what's the--
[electronic beep]

134
00:11:50,334 --> 00:11:51,335
[gasps]

135
00:11:53,629 --> 00:11:54,672
Oh no.

136
00:11:55,965 --> 00:11:58,676
What's going on, huh?
What's going on?

137
00:11:58,718 --> 00:12:00,094
Listen, I [stutters]--

138
00:12:01,011 --> 00:12:03,264
[electronic swoop]
[Melvin] Whoa!

139
00:12:05,057 --> 00:12:08,561
You, you just better watch
your step around here.

140
00:12:08,894 --> 00:12:11,230
I can't believe this
is happening to me.

141
00:12:11,647 --> 00:12:15,484
[gasps] Wait just a minute,
you stay away!

142
00:12:16,110 --> 00:12:20,865
This is your last warning! No!
No, no not so fast,

143
00:12:20,906 --> 00:12:23,284
Listen to me, stop, will ya.
[sobs]

144
00:12:23,409 --> 00:12:25,953
Parle vous Franscais?
Spreken ze Deutch?

145
00:12:26,036 --> 00:12:27,538
Stop! Whoa!

146
00:12:34,962 --> 00:12:37,047
