149
00:12:50,269 --> 00:12:51,270
[rings]

150
00:12:54,940 --> 00:12:55,941
[swish]

151
00:13:00,404 --> 00:13:01,405
[rings]

152
00:13:03,908 --> 00:13:04,909
[electronic swish]

153
00:13:06,035 --> 00:13:07,661
[Melvin panting]
[yelps]

154
00:13:11,373 --> 00:13:13,417
[panting continues]
[screams] No!

155
00:13:14,418 --> 00:13:15,419
[swishing continues]

156
00:13:15,961 --> 00:13:17,004
[stuttered gasps]

157
00:13:23,552 --> 00:13:26,972
Stop it! Don't hurt me please,
I beg of ya. [sobs]

158
00:13:29,475 --> 00:13:33,479
[panting] Ha-ha,
I know what, I'll

159
00:13:33,729 --> 00:13:35,689
give you this free of charge,

160
00:13:35,731 --> 00:13:38,025
