what do you say, huh?

161
00:13:40,027 --> 00:13:44,240
Yeah! Wait, wait a minute,
at least let me explain to ya.

162
00:13:44,240 --> 00:13:46,992
What you got here is your
most advanced stereophonic

163
00:13:47,034 --> 00:13:48,953
