of the forest

182
00:14:43,591 --> 00:14:44,717
into living puppets.

183
00:14:45,009 --> 00:14:46,594
What do you mean puppets?

184
00:14:47,219 --> 00:14:50,264
Just that. I turn them
into living puppets.

185
00:14:50,639 --> 00:14:53,851
But why would you want
to do something like that, huh?

186
00:14:53,893 --> 00:14:55,185
That's no concern of yours.

187
00:14:55,436 --> 00:14:58,230
Your job is to help me
locate the animals.

188
00:14:58,355 --> 00:15:01,317
Okay, okay,
it's your party, pal.

189
00:15:01,817 --> 00:15:04,445
Let's see, what have
we got here?

190
