209
00:16:04,129 --> 00:16:05,714
-Whoa!
-[screaming continues]

210
00:16:06,465 --> 00:16:07,466
[zapping]

211
00:16:09,218 --> 00:16:12,304
There he goes, there.
Quick, shoot him, shoot him!

212
00:16:12,554 --> 00:16:13,555
Come on.

213
00:16:15,265 --> 00:16:19,311
Whoa! Whoa! Watch out,
watch out, watch out!

214
00:16:19,353 --> 00:16:21,271
-Be quiet.
-[muffled screams]

215
00:16:29,697 --> 00:16:31,657
I told you to watch out.

216
00:16:32,616 --> 00:16:35,953
-Why didn't you listen to me?
-Oh, shut up!

217
00:16:37,955 --> 00:16:39,164
That's just great.

218
00:16:39,999 --> 00:16:43,002
I tried to save your neck
and you tell me to shut up.

219
00:16:43,168 --> 00:16:45,379
I don't like this relationship.

220
00:16:45,421 --> 00:16:47,172
-Listen, you little--
-Okay, okay.

221
00:16:48,674 --> 00:16:50,217
[running water]
[gentle music]

222
00:17:04,106 --> 00:17:05,107
[music continues]

223
00:17:20,164 --> 00:17:23,375
-[Melvin] Er, say boss?
-You may call me Toby.

224
00:17:23,459 --> 00:17:25,461
-Toby?
-That is my name.

225
00:17:25,878 --> 00:17:29,423
Well, Toby, once the animals
have been turned into living

226
00:17:29,465 --> 00:17:31,216
puppets, what's next?

227
00:17:31,383 --> 00:17:32,926
That is not for you to know.

228
00:17:33,052 --> 00:17:36,430
Ah, come on, I'm your pal,
you can tell me.

229
00:17:38,265 --> 00:17:39,975
-Can't you give me a hint?
-Shh.

230
00:17:40,434 --> 00:17:43,937
Be quiet, you fool,
the master is approaching.

231
00:17:45,773 --> 00:17:46,774
[Karuku] Toby.

232
00:17:49,234 --> 00:17:50,235
Toby.

233
00:17:52,362 --> 00:17:53,363
[yells] Toby.

234
00:17:54,823 --> 00:17:56,950
-[trembling]
-I'm here, Lord Karuku.

235
00:17:57,117 --> 00:17:58,952
Your wish is my command.

236
00:18:02,039 --> 00:18:06,251
I hope you have not
been lazy, Toby.

237
00:18:06,251 --> 00:18:07,294
